name: my best friend is dead
description: These lines represent my own words as lines. After generating 65 lines per iteration on a 5000x5000 image, these results perfectly fit the desired emotional outcome. In fact they were generated from SHA-512 hashes from my own personal poems. Intemporal and personal art, that is the main idea behind them. And no one will ever know what's written behind these lines, and how each one tends to fall to another.
